  "Subtitle": {
    "English": "Rapid Fire Starship Weapon",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "急速飞船武器",
    "TencentChinese": "急速飞船武器",
    "TraditionalChinese": "快速射擊太空船武器"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">rapid fire</span> starship weapon that launches superheated globes of liquid metal at hostile targets. These projectiles are <span class=\"name name-stellar\">extremely effective</span> against <span class=\"name name-stellar\">unshielded</span> starship hulls.<br><br>Note: the Accelerator's internal components are vulnerable to rapid <span class=\"name name-fuel\">overheating</span>. Sustained burst fire is not recommended.<br><br>Use <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> to change weapon mode. Press <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> to fire.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一种向敌对目标发射过热的液态金属球的<span class=\"name name-technology\">快速射击</span>飞船武器。这些射弹对<span class=\"name name-stellar\">无护盾</span>的船体有着<span class=\"name name-stellar\">极为有效</span>的杀伤力。<br><br>注意：加速器的内部构件容易受到快速<span class=\"name name-fuel\">过热</span>的影响。不建议连续射击。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span>变更武器模式。按下<span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span>发射。",
    "TencentChinese": "可短时快速连续开火。<br><br>容易过热，建议使用者开火时限制连发。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "向敵方目標<span class=\"name name-technology\">快速發射</span>超熱液態金屬球的太空船武器。這些射彈對付<span class=\"name name-stellar\">無防護罩</span>的太空船船身<span class=\"name name-stellar\">極為有效</span>。<br><br>注意：加速器的內部元件容易受快速<span class=\"name name-fuel\">過熱</span>的影響。不建議持續連射。<br><br>使用 <span class=\"name name-img\">CYCLEWEAPON</span> 即可切換武器模式。按住 <span class=\"name name-img\">SHIPFIRE</span> 即可開火。"
  },
